# Docker Compose for FIX API Adapter Development

## Quick Start

```bash
# Start all services
docker-compose up

# Start in background
docker-compose up -d

# Stop all services
docker-compose down

# Rebuild and start
docker-compose up --build
```

## Services

- **Frontend**: Next.js app on http://localhost:3000
- **Backend**: FastAPI on http://localhost:8000  
- **NATS**: Message broker on localhost:4222 (HTTP monitoring on 8222)

## Hot Reloading

All services support hot reloading:
- Frontend: Next.js dev server with Turbopack
- Backend: Uvicorn with --reload flag
- NATS: Alpine image with JetStream enabled

## Volumes

- Source code mounted for live development
- Node modules and Next.js cache excluded for performance
- Backend virtual environment cached
- NATS data and logs persisted
